## Summary of changes

1. **`api/v1beta1/clusterpodplacementconfig_webhook.go`** — Replaced the inline duplicate-architecture check in `validate()` with a call to `cppc.Spec.Plugins.NodeAffinityScoring.ValidateArchitecturesSet()`. Removed the unused `"errors"` import. `ValidateCreate` and `ValidateUpdate` both already delegate to `validate()`, so both paths are covered.

